判裁判費。\r\n中　　華　　民　　國　　111 　年　　10　　月　　5 　　日\r\n                  　　　　　　書記官　謝鎮光","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/PTEV/111%2c%e5%b1%8f%e5%b0%8f%2c357%2c20221005%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"PTEV,111,屏小,357,20221005,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"屏小","JNO":"357","JDATE":"20221005","JTITLE":"返還借款"}